narration_text: #C C washes pot lid in the sink
#C C puts utensils scrubber in kitchen sponge holder
#C C places the lid down in sink
#C C washes hand in sink
#C C picks cooking pot in the sink
#C C pours water in pot in the sink
#C C rinses the pot in sink
#C C carries the pot to cooker
#C C places pot on cooker
#C C walks back to sink
#C C picks pot lid in the sink
#C C rinses the lid with sink water
#C C turns off sink knob
#C C stands in front of the sink
#C C picks small skillet lid on countertop
#C C closes skillet on cooker with the lid
#C C picks pot lid in the sink
#C C turns on sink knob
#C C rinses the lid
#C C turns off sink knob
#C C shakes the lid on sink
#C C carries the lid to the cooker
#C C closes the pot in cooker with the lid
#C C wipes hand on kitchen towel on countertop
#C C stands
#C C lifts up both hands
#C C steps closer to sink
#C C operates camera on head
